Notes:
3:36 Glitch in the Matrix...
4:09 I am not sure if that sound was from water or something else. It was a Belgian road...
4:12 After 11 years of no-claim this stupidity damaged 2 rims and the front suspension (all fixed). In the end I only 1 shot made the edit...
4:20 It is normal here to drive on the emergency lane, when indicated above the road. It is a solution to the rapid growing amount of traffic. This car seemed to have stalled.
4:26 Here the open-to-traffic emergency lane changes to an exit. This car too ignored the open emergency lane and then took the exit very late.
4:45 This is collected packaging material that was of course put into the plastic bin afterwards.
